timeline.message:
initial implementation of the REST endpoint

implement parsing of communication diagrams in Compass
client implementation of the button
add tests and improve similarity calculation for communication diagrams
Merge branch 'develop' of https://github.com/ls1intum/Artemis into feature/plagiarism-check-modeling
improve consistency between text and modeling plagiarism checks
improve logs and use minimum similarity of 80% in text exercises
improve UML data model in compass
fix test after changing distance to similiarity
